00:21:36.190 --> 00:21:37.100
Lütfen!

00:21:38.190 --> 00:21:39.490
Baba!

00:21:50.920 --> 00:21:55.090
Dostum, ne Noel'di ama!

00:22:03.240 --> 00:22:06.020
Teşekkürler, Noel Baba...

